1
TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Nghin cu cc l hng ng dng web v cch phng chng
Tc gi lun vn: Honh Bch Kha: CH2012B
Ngi hng dn: TS. Trn c Khnh
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
Trong nhng nm gn y, s lng cc l hng bo mt web cng nh s
lng cc cuc tn cng mng ngy cng tng. c rt nhiu trang web b
nh sp, nhiu thng tin quan trng b nh cp, gy thit hi rt ln ti cc
doanh nghip. Mt trong nhng nguyn nhn ca tnh trng ny l do s tn ti
ca cc l hng an ninh trn cc ng dng web. V vy, tc gi chn ti
ny c th nghin cu cc l hng ny v a ra cc bin php khc phc,
phng chng cho cc lp trnh vin, qun tr vin website.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
- Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn: Nghin cu cc l hng an ninh ph bin
ca ng dng web trong nhng nm gn y t a ra cch phng chng cc
l hng ny cho lp trnh vin v qun tr vin website.
- i tng nghin cu: Mt s l hng an ninh ng dng web ph bin hin
nay.
- Phm vi nghin cu: Nghin cu c s l thuyt lin quan n nguyn nhn,
bn cht, cch khai thc t a ra cch phng chng, cch khc phc cc l
hng an ninh ng dng web ph bin hin nay. C th l cc l hng sau: SQL
Injection, XSS, CSRF, Directory Traversal, Padding Oracle.
c) Tm tt ni dung chnh v ng gp mi ca tc gi
- Ni dung chnh
o Tng quan v an ton thng tin mng my tnh
o Tng quan v cc l hng an ninh ng dng web
2
o Nghin cu khi nim, k thut tn cng t hiu c nguyn nhn,
bn cht v a ra cch phng chng cc l hng sau: SQL Injection,
XSS, CSRF, Directory Traversal, Padding Oracle.
o Xy dng h thng website th nghim vic tn cng v phng chng
cc l hng trn.
- ng gp ca tc gi
Tc gi nghin cu mt s l hng ng dng web ph bin hin nay t
a ra cch khc phc, phng chng cc l hng ny cho lp trnh vin, qun tr
vin website. Tc gi xy dng c h thng website th nghim cc l
hng. y l mi trng nghin cu vic tn cng v phng chng cc l hng
rt tt.
d) Phng php nghin cu
- Tng hp, phn tch v nh gi cc l hng an ninh ng dng web s dng cc
t liu tham kho.
- Xy dng cc h thng website th nghim t hiu su sc v bn cht v
a ra cch khc phc, phng chng cc l hng ny.
e) Kt lun
Lun vn nu r khi nim, cch thc tn cng khai thc cc l hng ng
dng web t hiu c nguyn nhn, bn cht ca cc l hng ny v a ra
cch phng chng hiu qu. Lun vn cng xy dng c h thng cc
website th nghim cc l hng bo mt. y l nhng kin thc rt cn thit
i cho cc lp trnh vin v qun tr vin website.
H Ni, ngy thng nm 2014
